🌐 Exciting News from Bharat Intern - My Second Project: Temperature Converter with CSS Animation! 🌡️

I am thrilled to share my latest achievement as a web developer at Bharat Intern! For my second project, I had the privilege of working on a Temperature Converter application that not only serves a practical purpose but also showcases my creative side with CSS animations. 🚀

🌡️ Temperature Conversion Made Easy:
The Temperature Converter is a user-friendly tool that allows you to seamlessly convert temperatures between Celsius and Fahrenheit. Whether you're planning a trip abroad or simply curious about the weather, this tool has got you covered. It's all about simplifying everyday tasks and making life a bit more convenient.

🎨 CSS Animation at its Finest:
To add a touch of elegance and interactivity to the Temperature Converter, I incorporated CSS animations. This not only enhances the user experience but also demonstrates my skills in frontend development. From smooth transitions to eye-catching effects, I've strived to make this project visually appealing and engaging.

🔗 Here's a sneak peek of some key features:
- Intuitive user interface for effortless temperature conversion.
- Real-time updates as you type, ensuring accuracy.
- Seamless transition between Celsius and Fahrenheit modes.
- CSS animations to provide a delightful user experience.

